commit.message: Fix deprecation warning regarding invalid escape sequences.

Merge pull request #4 from tvboxme/patch-1

Update flask.py
merge lookup conditions correctly using AND-logic
add `LOGGER_METHODS` setting to control logging via request-method

add `query_params` decorator

to avoid confusion, rename `query_<name>` method argument from
`query_params` to `params`.
use `crest` as REST client (instead of bare `requests`) in tests

improve Request and Response

1. add `scheme` and `uri` into Request
2. rename `content` to `data` in Response
3. log response info
use `method_decorator` to decorate Class-based views in Django

update Documentation

1. add `Quickstart`
2. rename `resource` to `rsrc` in demo code
add essential CORS headers for actual requests
support HTTP method `OPTIONS` and Cross-Origin Resource Sharing (CORS)
get query parameters from `request.GET.iterlists()` in Django

update requirements

1. remove non-core dependent libraries from "setup.py"
2. split "requirements.txt" into "requirements.txt" and "requirements-dev.txt"
